ts, tags, and attributes from inner data\n- get: alternate initializer\n\nDeprecations:\n\n- remove_tags: (as of 1.0) use strip\n\nExamples:\n\n```\nfrom gazpacho import Soup\n\nhtml = \"<div><p class='a'>1</p><p class='a'>2</p><p class='b'>3</p></div>\"\nurl = \"https://www.gazpacho.xyz\"\n\nsoup = Soup(html)\nsoup = Soup.get(url)\n```"]}], "exports": []}]}